{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0001", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0001", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 1}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "Cyber hygiene is indispensable for financial stability. It is not only about technical solutions such as passwords and firewalls, but also about good governance. Anyone who does not have their digital foundation in order endangers business operations, reputation and financial health.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "The European NIS2 directive makes digital security a task for the board. It's about more than IT: business continuity, risks and integrity are at stake. A cyber incident can halt production, lose customers and lead to legal claims. Good governance also means taking responsibility for digital security.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "Cyber security has direct consequences for financial reporting and corporate position:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "- Accountants test continuity in the annual accounts. Without demonstrable safety, comments or limitations arise in the audit report.\n- Customers and partners are increasingly demanding digital security in contracts. Anyone who cannot provide proof of a safely operating organization runs the risk of losing orders. The chain clauses from NIS2 make this even more urgent.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "## The basics are in order with demonstrable cyber hygiene", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "A good digital foundation starts with structural measures that you can also demonstrate. The NIS2 Quality Mark is a quality mark that proves that your company meets security standards. Independent control ensures trust among customers and partners.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Cyber security is more than technology. It protects your data, your reputation and your financial stability. Organizations that invest in digital security not only protect their data, but also their reputation, their customers and their future.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://www.samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "- Do you have an SME company and do you want to reduce your cyber risks? Then take a look at [Cyber ​​Fundament](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-voor-het-mkb/), especially for SME entrepreneurs.\n- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) especially for large businesses and reduce your cyber risks.\n- Do you also want to [do business safely](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link)? View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars.\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit", "source_title": "Digital risks for your financial stability", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/digitale-risicos-voor-jouw-financiele-stabiliteit.html", "source_date": "2025-11-17", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
